name: World Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery Congress
content: Join the World Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery Congress in Dubai, UAE (Dec 07-09, 2023). Experience groundbreaking advancements, innovative techniques, and cutting-edge research. Connect with experts, engage in discussions, and explore dental implants, reconstructive surgery, orthognathic surgery, and more. Embrace collaboration, interdisciplinary exchange, and the vibrant atmosphere of Dubai. Register now to shape the future of oral and maxillofacial surgery.
